title: Deadly Heat
tooltip: universal property: extreme heat, creatures become resistant to cold
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

While on a [[plane]] with this property, a creature is subject to extreme heat. In addition, all creatures gain resistance to [[cold damage|damage type]], and a creature that is usually resistant to cold damage becomes immune to it.